title: [Weekly-33] 2019.12.15
content:
Weekly visual project - 2019/12/15
The excerpt I thrive on stress and begin to pine if there is no deadline. Otherwise—if I may be presumptuous: I was born like the sentry in Goethe’s Faust II:
Zum Sehen geboren
Zum Schauen bestellt
(“Born to see, my task is to watch”)
by Peter Drucker
